    { "area": "Retry and timeout policies", "evolution_path": "Per-step retry policies (exponential backoff, max attempts) can be configured independently. Compensation steps should retry indefinitely with alerts — partial compensation is worse than retrying." },
    { "area": "Parallel steps", "evolution_path": "If future requirements allow Inventory + Payment in parallel, the state machine can be extended to a DAG. Keep it sequential until proven necessary." }
